sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser Client<br/>(localhost:5173)
    participant CORS as CORS Guard
    participant Server as Axum Server<br/>(127.0.0.1:8765)
    participant ConnMgr as Connection Manager<br/>(AppState)
    participant Broadcast as Broadcast Channel
    participant GameSvc as Game Service<br/>(trait object)

    Note over Browser,GameSvc: Genre Discovery (before game starts)
    Browser->>CORS: GET /api/genres
    CORS-->>Browser: 403 Forbidden (if wrong origin)
    CORS->>Server: pass through (localhost:5173)
    Server->>Server: scan genre_packs/ directory
    Server-->>Browser: 200 { "mutant_wasteland": { "worlds": [...] } }

    Note over Browser,GameSvc: Player Connection
    Browser->>Server: GET /ws (WebSocket upgrade)
    Server->>Server: generate PlayerId (UUID v4)
    Server->>ConnMgr: add_connection(player_id, sender)
    Server-->>Browser: 101 Switching Protocols

    Note over Browser,GameSvc: Real-Time Message Exchange
    Browser->>Server: text frame (JSON GameMessage)
    Server->>Server: deserialize GameMessage
    alt valid message
        Server->>GameSvc: (dispatch — story 2-5)
    else invalid JSON
        Server-->>Browser: ERROR GameMessage
    end

    Note over Browser,GameSvc: Server Broadcast (e.g. narration)
    GameSvc->>Broadcast: broadcast(GameMessage)
    Broadcast-->>Browser: text frame (all connected clients)

    Note over Browser,GameSvc: Graceful Shutdown
    Server->>Server: Ctrl+C → oneshot signal
    Server->>Server: finish in-flight requests
    Server->>ConnMgr: remove all connections
    Server->>Server: process exits cleanly